Angkat kaki awak.

472
00:39:36,918 --> 00:39:37,918
Terima kasih.

473
00:39:40,968 --> 00:39:42,848
Apa yang awak buat?

474
00:39:47,098 --> 00:39:48,228
Sebenarnya...

475
00:39:51,188 --> 00:39:52,898
- Pergi.
- Mari kita balik.

476
00:39:52,978 --> 00:39:54,898
- Ke tepi.
- Saya benci tikus!

477
00:39:57,108 --> 00:39:58,318
Yeong-ro, cepat.

478
00:39:58,448 --> 00:39:59,648
Saya hampir siap.

479
00:40:06,998 --> 00:40:10,618
Saya bersumpah
saya nampak tikus di sana.

480
00:40:10,708 --> 00:40:12,998
Saya memang nampak seekor
yang masuk ke sana.

481
00:40:14,458 --> 00:40:16,298
Awak tak tahu peraturan asrama?

482
00:40:16,588 --> 00:40:18,128
Berani awak menjerit begitu?

483
00:40:18,208 --> 00:40:20,088
Maafkan saya, puan.

484
00:40:23,088 --> 00:40:25,258
Awak kata awak nampak,
jadi pastikan awak tangkap.

485
00:40:32,768 --> 00:40:34,108
Saya seorang diri?

486
00:40:55,288 --> 00:40:56,288
Eun Yeong-ro.

487
00:40:56,998 --> 00:40:58,248
Ya, puan?

488
00:41:00,258 --> 00:41:01,798
Kenapa awak berpeluh-peluh?

489
00:41:03,798 --> 00:41:07,848
Saya berlari supaya tak lewat
untuk sesi panggil nama.

490
00:41:08,308 --> 00:41:10,388
Jadi, kenapa awak
perlu balik lewat?

491
00:41:10,978 --> 00:41:13,558
Macam mana kalau rakan sebilik
awak dibuang disebabkan awak?

492
00:41:15,108 --> 00:41:18,268
Maafkan saya.
Saya takkan balik lewat lagi.

493
00:41:20,858 --> 00:41:22,238
Bilik 207.

494
00:41:23,528 --> 00:41:25,528
Baca peraturan asrama.

495
00:41:26,198 --> 00:41:27,368
- Patuh waktu perintah berkurung.
- Patuh waktu perintah berkurung.

496
